	<h1 class="title">手机输入法要怎么赚钱？这个应用说导购、叫车都没问题</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/97532/small/97532.jpeg?1431064746" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">赵长存 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-22 08:52:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13696/medium/13696.jpg?1439891292" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13696" data-title="《手机输入法要怎么赚钱？这个应用说导购、叫车都没问题》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13696/medium/13696.jpg?1439891292" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13696.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
